snippet.title: NES Longplay [198] Dragon Warrior II
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: Valis77

 This is my least favorite Dragon Quest game ever. It's so difficult and frustrating. As usual with editing i level up off screen and im not gonna play this this version of DQ II anytime soon. My least favorite DQ game. -
